{"tid":2335487,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：個人權利沒可能凌駕整體社會利益　","createTime":"2020-12-22T02:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T04:06:30.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"882363df330c9d0b08ed2e9a5a5e9a26e21d0a0a","tid":2335487,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:36:47.000Z","msg":"終審法院就《緊急條例》和《禁蒙面規例》的司法覆核，裁定政府終極上訴得直。行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊表示，對結果不感到太出奇，一直認為處理這些問題涉及平衡測試，個人權利沒有可能凌駕於整體社會利益。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，現時要留意的是執法機關在執行方面如何處理，按他理解，當申訴人在初審勝訴時，警方已宣布暫緩執行《禁蒙面規例》，至今似乎未有改動。現時在疫情下各人都要戴口罩，屬合理辯解。<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人陳皓桓在同一節目說，團體向警方提出要舉辦遊行與集會時，警方可施加條件，故不需要用《禁蒙面規例》的大框架，規管所有合法遊行與集會。他說一些同性戀或跨性別人士可能想在不露面容的情況下，參與同志遊行表達權益，《禁蒙面規例》或令他們卻步。"},{"pid":"b3ae7b3baf7a6967d0fcfe0d5dfa7af4da3e29a6","tid":2335487,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:37:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566564-20201222.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566564-20201222.htm&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FdjJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=83e38f38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566564-20201222.htm&h=84850854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566564-20201222.htm</a>"},{"pid":"245d434702361577fca06a0377ab5c9f2caa095b","tid":2335487,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:37:59.000Z","msg":"湯家驊：禁蒙面法裁決反映社會利益較個人權利較重要<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】行政會議成員資深大律師湯家驊表示，終院裁定禁蒙面法合憲，反映法院同意社會整體利益較個人權利重要；又指檢控須證明當事人相關犯罪意圖，不認為蒙面參與集會便能入罪。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊：「任何犯法都要證明犯罪意圖，如果他意圖搗亂一個公開和平集會，我覺得執行法例是沒有問題。如果你證實不了他意圖搗亂和平集會，我又看不到為何能夠入罪。據我理解，申訴人初審勝訴時，警方已宣布暫停執行禁蒙面法，今日為止暫緩執行的決定未有改動。」<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊亦稱，根據終院判決，緊急法下立禁蒙面法不一定要交由立法會討論，但認為長遠而言，禁蒙面法應透過立法會作討論及處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=417504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417504&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FdjJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=4d368b15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417504&h=2e0552d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=417504</a>"},{"pid":"1b66b3b51251b92415ab9b1467b8a90abcdd323b","tid":2335487,"uid":11291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:38:15.000Z","msg":"11哥收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58089f104d4ec05a97f8526e638192e574a15298","tid":2335487,"uid":265731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"但係個人食幻幻權利可以凌駕社會道德"},{"pid":"a931b3cb6d49eba78fc926999ab46f4c9972046e","tid":2335487,"uid":130797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:45:09.000Z","msg":"幻幻既個人權利<br />\n係唔可能凌駕整體男士既利益<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45a1bc17fb022ba3d4420abefa9cff5129fbfc2","tid":2335487,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:46:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">鄧小強呢？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b1bffe52c75e4783e83e3afc4aa547de2de78ca9","tid":2335487,"uid":325716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:47:46.000Z","msg":"陳同佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988e3170d00f0e087f7373fdef308d32a4beebb1","tid":2335487,"uid":82935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n<br />\n林奠政府 同 三萬隻狗既 個人權利沒可能凌駕整體社會利益 <br />\n班撼港產賣港賊 搞到香港無法無天"},{"pid":"3b317573f8dbf592cddd0aa3ce73b356aacec694","tid":2335487,"uid":45450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:49:35.000Z","msg":"將誠哥副